extends course-layout.pug

block content
  section.jumbotron.text-center
    .container
      h1.jumbotron-heading Mathematics
      p.lead.text-muted
        | Whether you need a refresher, or need to learn something that you did not know before, we have you covered with all of the mathematics that you need to know.
  .album.py-5.bg-light
    .container
      .row
        .col-md-4
          .card.mb-4.box-shadow
            .card-body
              h3 Algebra
              p.card-text
                | Algebra is one of the most basic tools needed to learn how to speak the language of physics.
              .d-flex.justify-content-between.align-items-center
                .btn-group
                  button.btn.btn-sm.btn-outline-secondary(type='button', onclick="location.href = '/algebra';") Start
                //small.text-muted 9 mins
        .col-md-4
          .card.mb-4.box-shadow
            .card-body
              h3 Geometry
              p.card-text
                | All about triangles, and how to calculate distances and stuff with triangles and angles. 
              .d-flex.justify-content-between.align-items-center
                .btn-group
                  button.btn.btn-sm.btn-outline-secondary(type='button', onclick="location.href = '/geometry';") Start
                //small.text-muted 9 mins
        .col-md-4
          .card.mb-4.box-shadow
            .card-body
              h3 Calculus
              p.card-text
                | The mathematics of change, namely rates of change. This will give you the ability to calculate things that change. 
              .d-flex.justify-content-between.align-items-center
                .btn-group
                  button.btn.btn-sm.btn-outline-secondary(type='button', onclick="location.href = '/calculus';") Start
                //small.text-muted 9 mins
